devdoc.details: Need to support Certificate Of Ownership (ownership information in COO - JSON Web Token stored on IPFS like the COA). Support of COO will make the NFT transferable to another portfolio/Chain (unchained NFT: burned from origin and created at destination): can be moved to another compatible portfolios/wallets.

CoaURISet(uint256,string).details: Emitted when a Certificate Of Authority is set for a tokenId (location).

allTokens().details: Get _allTokens array with tokenIds used in Portfolio.

burn(uint256).details: Destroys 'tokenId'. Emits an event 'trasnfer'. Current implementation is still burning an NFT. Should become moving out an NFT (move an nft from one location to another one).Still using the owner concept of ERC721. Should be replaced by COO JSON Web Token signed (Verifiable Credential).Requirements: whenNotPaused and onlyOwner. 'tokenId' must exist.

params.tokenId: Location of NFT to be burned.

getAllTokenIds().details: Get all TokenIds with an NFT: verifiable credentials COA and COO.

getCoaURI(uint256).details: Get COA URI for a tokenId if tokenId exists. Current implementation of COA URI is IPFS-CID of COARequirements: TokenId must exist.

mint(address,string).details: Mint an NFT. Current implementation does not have the Certificate of Ownership. Should become MOVE an NFT to toa new location in the portfolio.Still using the owner concept of ERC721. Should be replaced by COO JSON Web Token signed (Verifiable Credential).Requirements: whenNotPaused and onlyOwner.

params._coaURI: URI of COA - Current implementation is IPFS-CID of COA.
params.recipient: address of owner - current implementation it is an ethereum address. Should be a DID.

returns._0: uint256:new tokenId (new location where NFT is stored).

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: Pause all token transfers (mint - burn), setPortfolioURI and setCoaURI.Requirements: whenNotPaused and onlyOwner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

portfolioInfo().details: Get Portfolio info: owner, name, symbol, portfolio URI, total supply.

returns._0: array with information: address:owner, string:name, string:symbol , string:portfolioURI, uint256:totalSupply

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setCoaURI(uint256,string).details: Get COA URI for a tokenId if tokenId exists and emits an event 'CoaURISet'. Current implementation of COA URI is IPFS-CID of COA.Requirements: whenNotPaused and onlyOwner. 'tokenId' must exist.

params._coaURI: URI of COA - Current implementation is IPFS-CID of COA.

setPortfolioURI(string).details: Set Portfolio URI and emits an event 'PortfolioURISet'.Requirements: whenNotPaused and onlyOwner

params.portfolioURI_: URI of the portfolio - current implementation IPFS-CID of image.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: Unpause all token transfers (mint - burn), setPortfolioURI and setCoaURI.Requirements: whenPaused and onlyOwner.
